            <p>A new Dead Rising game is reportedly in development.</p>
<p>While there's been no formal word of a follow-up game, <a href="https://mp1st.com/news/new-dead-rising-game-development-set-in-hollywood">mp1st</a> claims Capcom has another "major" Dead Rising project in the works, reportedly set in Hollywood.</p>
